    "E2 suggested that generating insights based on awaring of user behavior would enhance the execution of tasks.",
    "Additionally, E3 noted the significant reduction in manual effort due to AI generation, stating, \"Previously, using PowerBI required a lot of time and operations, but now it only takes a sentence.",
